originContent: This project uses the [OpenAI ChatGPT API](https://openai.com/api/) (specifically, gpt-3.5-turbo) and [Vercel Edge functions](https://vercel.com/features/edge-functions) with streaming and [Upstash](https://console.upstash.com/) for Redis cache and rate limiting.
